doList:['Apply grain overlay at 3-8% opacity — barely perceptible','Use SVG noise filter for scalable, performant grain','Use warm, muted colors that complement the analog texture','Pair with humanist or slightly organic typefaces','Use warm whites and off-whites for backgrounds','Keep the overall design clean — grain is texture, not clutter'],
