doList:['Use serif typeface for all text elements','Set body text at 18-20px for screen readability','Use generous line-height (1.6-1.8)','Apply warm, muted background colors (cream, off-white)','Use spacious margins and vertical rhythm','Add drop caps or pull quotes for editorial rhythm'],
